Class BenchmarkMethodInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.maxur.perfmodel.backend.service.BenchmarkMethodInterceptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.aopalliance.aop.Advice, org.aopalliance.intercept.Interceptor, org.aopalliance.intercept.MethodInterceptor

    public class BenchmarkMethodInterceptor
extends Object
implements org.aopalliance.intercept.MethodInterceptor
    This is an interceptor that will implement benchmark of method latency.

    This interceptor does not import any hk2 API and thus is a pure AOP Alliance method interceptor that might be used in any software that enabled AOP Alliance interceptors
